QuestData.Title: Medical Supplies
QuestData.Description: We need supplies to tend to our wounded, but the supply crates containing them were scattered in the crash. If you can bring back any crates you find, I would be very grateful.
QuestData.CompletionText: Did you find the boxes I spoke of?
QuestData.RewardText: These will do perfectly. I'll get my medics to work immediately.$B$BThank you.
